  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this game, you can craft a fascinating, surprising, and memorable life story with the simplest operation—just choosing one card per turn.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You'll encounter many challenges as well as opportunities. Seize those opportunities and overcome seemingly difficult challenges!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Examples of in-game combos:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Automatically synthesizing materials to build a rocket.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3393750/extras/e8c5751eaaa294122c8cf66afd68eec8.poster.avif?t=1770173333\" width=800 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3393750/extras/e8c5751eaaa294122c8cf66afd68eec8.webm?t=1770173333\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3393750/extras/e8c5751eaaa294122c8cf66afd68eec8.mp4?t=1770173333\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Terrorist attacks happening worldwide.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3393750/extras/3c073864557b2bcf10faeb37e778520d.poster.avif?t=1770173333\" width=800 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3393750/extras/3c073864557b2bcf10faeb37e778520d.webm?t=1770173333\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3393750/extras/3c073864557b2bcf10faeb37e778520d.mp4?t=1770173333\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are many different gameplay styles waiting for you to explore.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >For instance, as you age, you'll need to face various [stages] of choices, where different decisions could completely alter your life's trajectory.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You'll encounter various [events] that could either bring you benefits or present challenges you must overcome.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When your [badges] level up, the choices and gameplay in life will become even more diverse or take a different turn.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Come and enjoy playing out your life!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you wish to contact us, you can join our QQ group: 817959767.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this game, you can craft a fascinating, surprising, and memorable life story with the simplest operation—just choosing one card per turn.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You'll encounter many challenges as well as opportunities. Seize those opportunities and overcome seemingly difficult challenges!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Examples of in-game combos:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Automatically synthesizing materials to build a rocket.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3393750/extras/e8c5751eaaa294122c8cf66afd68eec8.poster.avif?t=1770173333\" width=800 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3393750/extras/e8c5751eaaa294122c8cf66afd68eec8.webm?t=1770173333\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3393750/extras/e8c5751eaaa294122c8cf66afd68eec8.mp4?t=1770173333\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Terrorist attacks happening worldwide.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3393750/extras/3c073864557b2bcf10faeb37e778520d.poster.avif?t=1770173333\" width=800 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3393750/extras/3c073864557b2bcf10faeb37e778520d.webm?t=1770173333\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3393750/extras/3c073864557b2bcf10faeb37e778520d.mp4?t=1770173333\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are many different gameplay styles waiting for you to explore.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >For instance, as you age, you'll need to face various [stages] of choices, where different decisions could completely alter your life's trajectory.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You'll encounter various [events] that could either bring you benefits or present challenges you must overcome.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When your [badges] level up, the choices and gameplay in life will become even more diverse or take a different turn.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Come and enjoy playing out your life!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you wish to contact us, you can join our QQ group: 817959767.</p>",
